ui.outputpanels

Class DataRep

  • java.lang.Object
    • ui.outputpanels.DataRep

  • public class DataRep
extends java.lang.Object
    This class keep track of the mathematical data, which are not directly related to the solving process, of the ODEWorkspace. This includes the WorkspaceData, the file, the ode text, and the variable keeper.
    Author:
    Clinic 10-11, modified from Clinic 08-09
